Interface IPartialOrder

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<IPartialOrder>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ICloseOrder, IFillOrder

    public interface IPartialOrder
extends java.lang.Comparable<IPartialOrder>
    Contains partial order data (either fill or close) when order was partially or fully filled or closed by server, respectively.
    Order's lifecycle contains from 0 to many elements of this data.
    See Also:
    IFillOrder, ICloseOrder, IOrder.getFillHistory(), IOrder.getCloseHistory()
